<div id="country3" class="tabcontent">
<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>Acknowledgment Form</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen captures the details of acknowledgement. When item is issued against indent then receiving department stock is updated only after acknowledgement.
<br /><hr /><br />

<img src="images/ST_ACK.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />
<p>
<span class="title">Issue department: </span><br />
Select issue department from the list.
<br />
<span class="title">Acknowledgement Date: </span> <br />
Current date will be displayed by the system.
<br />
<span class="title">Acknowledge by: </span> 
<br />Select acknowledge by from the list.

<br />
    <span class="title">Receipt department: </span> 
    <br />By default current login department will be displayed.
<br />
    <span class="title">Issue No.: </span> 
    <br />Select issue no. from the list. All issue no. which is not acknowledged will be displayed in the list.
<br />
    <span class="title">Issue date: </span> 
    <br />Issue date will be displayed based on issue no.
<br />
    <span class="title">Submit (Button): </span> 
    <br />By clicking on submit button Item issued against selected issue no. will be displayed in details grid.
<br />
    <span class="title">Accept (Button): </span> 
    <br />By clicking on accept button stock will be updated for receipt/login department.


</div>
